category: sans-serif
subsets: menu,latin,latin-ext

family: Armata

designer: Viktoriya Grabowska

approved: true
description: <p>Armata is a low contrast sans \
  serif text face. In Aramata we find a mixture \
  of a the familiar shapes and an aesthetic \
  steadiness and strength with a small number \
  of innovative and delicate gestures. Armata \
  can be used in a wide range of sizes.</p>

font.Armata-Regular.ttf.style: normal
font.Armata-Regular.ttf.weight: 400

